            <h2>Rifle Team</h2>
            The Rifle Team is one of our most intense and best teams. Not only do cadets have to learn how to operate an air rifle, they also have to remain consistent and disciplined through out thier journey as this team requires intense commiment and dedication. Cadets will devote multiple hours in physical and mental Training. If you are up to the challange then, Good luck.
            <br>
            Team Leader: Paula
            <br>
            Member Count: 11
        </TextImg>
        <div class="margin"/>
        <TextImg image="" altTxt="Not sure what to put here - Cadet Ibarra" backgroundColor="#F1F0EA" order={0} align = "right" color="black">
            <h2 style="color:black;">Academic Team</h2>
            The academics team is made up of the entire unit. No one leads the academic team. Our goal is to get our best grades that we can. Honestly im not sure about this team - Cadet Ibarra
            <br>
            Team Leader: Nobody
            <br>
            Member Count: Entire Unit
        </TextImg>
